e":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"槍決ok?"},{"pid":"3a26dce76b5f781a47b95e0e29107253e3a2409e","tid":1849432,"uid":81478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee2a6dce6041e1d606b58e89df62f75fe4873e0f","tid":1849432,"uid":201374,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"8191c733af3901a784db306bc0f825e40415e4d3","tid":1849432,"uid":17506,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會係有d人專登咁講博快d有得醫?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"似係驚自己中咗招係唔係都話武漢返,咁先可以check吓係咪中招<br />\n同埋柒婆條撚樣話中武肺唔使錢,佢哋可能覺得聲稱自己中咗都唔使錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"琴日條友唔係講返話要錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"6559f77b005ff4f6cbacb849395658c616be517a","tid":1849432,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"有冇咁撚多畜生去武漢呀"},{"pid":"15ad5275feae4c33397ab762027880c0e59386df","tid":1849432,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe9ade18728d034b3d625315b5c6f7aecf34ac9b","tid":1849432,"uid":229886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"屌你青衣都搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"封島"},{"pid":"ff5ee12375d406163d59d0a86c17c6fdafb50275","tid":1849432,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"743fca5518f4beda162f4bb1231ad374ed905bb1","tid":1849432,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"槍決ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/SJLpUGP.gif\" />"},{"pid":"85d9083fe92702c95318b8443dbcf1f9dc6b770f","tid":1849432,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"話自己武漢返黎有事冇事都隔離14日先<br />\n以為咁講會快d見到醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clo